Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.13,1:01:38.88,nen den,,0,0,0,,Đi.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.06,1:01:47.81,nen den,,0,0,0,,Sư thúc.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.81,1:01:49.22,nen den,,0,0,0,,Mau đưa sư huynh đi.
