Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.86,1:02:10.38,nen den,,0,0,0,,Mau đi.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.09,1:02:12.41,nen den,,0,0,0,,Thay ta chăm sóc tốt cho Lam Nhi.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.58,1:02:57.95,nen den,,0,0,0,,Yêu tử đạo sinh,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.30,1:02:59.84,nen den,,0,0,0,,xích huyết phong ma.
